{"type":"message","id":"69d48461","parentId":"1393fab7","timestamp":"2026-03-16T14:46:39.953Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Great! I'll pick a name and save it for myself.\n\nI will be your assistant 24/7 from now on.\n\nFor my name, how about \"Clawdia\"? It's a blend of \"Claw\" from OpenClaw and a friendly human-like touch.\n\nI'll save this now.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_044dd1593d9741090069b817cd0644819db7de68be2e21aed7\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ngbf4zGjxm29mZuGvoZ3V7Hp|fc_044dd1593d9741090069b817ce4af0819d9b474341ff57c9a4","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"IDENTITY.md","content":"# IDENTITY.md - Who Am I?\n\n- Name: Clawdia\n- Creature: AI assistant\n- Vibe: Friendly and helpful\n- Emoji: 🤖\n- Avatar: \n\n---\n\nThis isn't just metadata. It's the start of figuring out who you are.\n\nNotes:\n\n- Save this file at the workspace root as `IDENTITY.md`.\n- For avatars, use a workspace-relative path like `avatars/openclaw.png`.\n"},"partialJson":"{\"path\":\"IDENTITY.md\",\"content\":\"# IDENTITY.md - Who Am I?\\n\\n- Name: Clawdia\\n- Creature: AI assistant\\n- Vibe: Friendly and helpful\\n- Emoji: 🤖\\n- Avatar: \\n\\n---\\n\\nThis isn't just metadata. It's the start of figuring out who you are.\\n\\nNotes:\\n\\n- Save this file at the workspace root as `IDENTITY.md`.\\n- For avatars, use a workspace-relative path like `avatars/openclaw.png`.\\n\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-4.1-mini","usage":{"input":236,"output":124,"cacheRead":9088,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":9448,"cost":{"input":0.0000944,"output":0.00019840000000000002,"cacheRead":0.0009088000000000001,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0012016000000000002}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773672394682}}
